ai_analysis.brief: On the 1 hour chart price is trading near recent highs with bullish momentum and expanding volatility. Short term moving averages are aligned bullish and momentum indicators favor buyers while RSI is elevated but not at extreme sustained overbought. Support sits near 3590 and 3550 while resistance and recent swing highs cluster around 3675 and 3740.
ai_analysis.detailed: Price is above the 20 and 50 period EMAs and is testing the upper Bollinger Band which indicates strong short term buying pressure. MACD on the 1 hour is positive with the MACD line above its signal line and the histogram showing expanding bullish bars which supports momentum continuation. Volume has increased on up moves and market sentiment reads bullish which makes a tactical buy with a tight stop under 3590 a logical risk managed approach.
